<h4>headcanons</h4>

<p>- She keeps a notepad of paper where she often draws out her emotions & feelings through pictures, her version of a diary, just using pictures instead of words.

<p>- She cuts her own hair.

<p>- She's 5'2.

<p>- Their family is Swiss, via the Morgenstern side.

<p>- Has an affinity for vintage/vintage feel clothes

<p>- can’t make eggs & doesn’t like them

<p>- didn’t drink underage except for a bottle of kailua she & simon smuggled from his mom at 13

</li>

