<p>

<div id="left"><img src="https://i.imgur.com/HHdVBdm.png"></div>
<a href="#?w=458" rel="c01" class="poplight" title="full verse description, headcanons, & ship info, as well as verse-specific notes, world-building, glossary, & triggers as-needed."><b>verse details</b>.</a> &mdash; following the events of The Shadowhunter Chronicles, but keeps a touch of the canon established in Freeform's Shadowhunters. Compliant with deviations on the show on a plotted basis only.    

<br><br>

<p><center><h4>canon variants</h4></center>

<p><center><h3><b>raised in the clave</b><br> (alt.) raised as a nephilim</h3></center>
<p>
<div id="left"><img src="https://i.imgur.com/HHdVBdm.png"></div>
<a href="#?w=458" rel="cv01" class="poplight" title="full verse description, headcanons, & ship info, as well as verse-specific notes, world-building, glossary, & triggers as-needed."><b>VERSE DETAILS</b>.</a> &mdash; based on the world-building established in the shadowhunter chronicles as well as some influence of freeform's shadowunters. this follows a variant what-if regarding what could have happened following the Uprising had Jocelyn decided to raise her children within the clave.

<br>

<p><center><h3><b>evening star</b><br> (alt.) centurion</h3></center>
<p>

<div id="left"><img src="https://i.imgur.com/HHdVBdm.png"></div>
<a href="#?w=458" rel="cv02" class="poplight" title="full verse description, headcanons, & ship info, as well as verse-specific notes, world-building, glossary, & triggers as-needed."><b>VERSE DETAILS</b>.</a> &mdash; glorious was supposed to save them, but instead of severing Jace's connection to Jonathan, Clary was forced to watch both her soulmate & her brother die on that field. moving on proved nearly impossible, so instead she would go on to do the unthinkable. throwing herself into her training, she'd make herself into something that would be face that kind of choice again - she became a centurion.

<br>

<p><center><h3><b>Ördögház</b><br> (alt.) raised by vampires</h3></center>
<p>
<div id="left"><img src="https://i.imgur.com/HHdVBdm.png"></div>
<a href="#?w=458" rel="cv03" class="poplight" title="full verse description, headcanons, & ship info, as well as verse-specific notes, world-building, glossary, & triggers as-needed."><b>VERSE DETAILS</b>.</a> &mdash; after Jocelyn fled with her unborn daughter & knowing Valentine wasn't truly dead, she realized she was in no position to keep her daughter safe. seeking out help, she found it in the head of the Hungarian vampire clan - Sonja. Clary would go on to be raised as the only human within the clan, learning unique abilities aongside the vampires & death dealers before returning to Idris on her 16th birthday when the truth of her parentage came out.

<br>

<p><center><h3><b>charlotte adele</b><br> (alt.) duplicate verse!</h3></center>
<p>
<div id="left"><img src="https://i.imgur.com/HHdVBdm.png"></div>
<a href="#?w=458" rel="cv04" class="poplight" title="full verse description, headcanons, & ship info, as well as verse-specific notes, world-building, glossary, & triggers as-needed."><b>VERSE DETAILS</b>.</a> &mdash; coming soon! born <b>charlotte adele</b>, charlie is the twin sister to one Jonathan Morgenstern & big sister to one Clary Fairchild. as the oldest girl in the Fairchild clan's next generation, she takes her job as big sister <b>very</b> seriously. verse is default for interaction with duplicate muses.

