<center><h3><b>I still believe in heroes</b><br>
marvel cinematic universe</h3></center>
<p>

<div id="left"><img src="https://i.imgur.com/HHdVBdm.png"></div>
<a href="#?w=458" rel="f01" class="poplight" title="full verse description, headcanons, & ship info, as well as verse-specific notes, world-building, glossary, & triggers as-needed."><b>VERSE DETAILS</b>.</a> &mdash; After losing the love of her life during the battle of the burren, Clary isolated herself from the friends & family she'd gained in her short time as a Shadowhunter. When the opportunity to train as a centurion presented itself, she took it, becoming an elite warrior of the Clave. Five years later, in 2013, the convergence changed everything all over again & she found herself wandering through a very different new york than the one she had once left behind. now, instead of a shadowhunter, she's a <b>shield agent</b>.

<br /><br />
<center><h3><b>tempered & balanced</b><br>
hogwarts herbology professor</h3></center>
<p>

<div id="left"><img src="https://i.imgur.com/HHdVBdm.png"></div>
<a href="#?w=458" rel="f02" class="poplight" title="full verse description, headcanons, & ship info, as well as verse-specific notes, world-building, glossary, & triggers as-needed."><b>VERSE DETAILS</b>.</a> &mdash; at Hogwarts School of Witchcraft & Wizardry. After her graduation from Hogwarts, Clary worked as an editor for a prestigious research journal regarding herbology. It seemed like a cushy enough job in theory, but between the long hours of editing others’ work & not being able to do her own research or have the freedom to pursue creative avenues. She eventually left this job to take up a position within Hogwarts as one of the Herbology professors. She eventually would go on to become head of the department, as well as instructing art as an extracurricular class.


<br /><br />
<center><h3><b>my way in the universe</b><br>
star wars (multi arc verse)</h3></center>
<p>

<div id="left"><img src="https://i.imgur.com/HHdVBdm.png"></div>
<a href="#?w=458" rel="f03" class="poplight" title="full verse description, headcanons, & ship info, as well as verse-specific notes, world-building, glossary, & triggers as-needed."><b>VERSE DETAILS</b></a> &mdash; sequestered away from even all but the highest levels of the resistance, Clary is a force-sensitive human with a unique ability to imbue crystals with specific abilities through the Force. what might take a Jedi days, meditating over the crystals, she can do in a fraction of the time, but often at a great & terrible cost. 

<blockquote>
    <p><b>note:</b> primarily set in the <b>sequels</b> era, but with arcs for prequels & original trilogy.
</blockquote>


