<li class="active">
<h4>description</h4>
<p>this verse follows the canon outlined in her <b>main biography</b> & contains the events from the original six book series, <i>the mortal instruments</i>. 

<br />
<br />
<br />
<br />
</li>

<li>
<h4>notes on interaction</h4>

<p><b>option i.</b> meeting after she joins the institute.
<blockquote>
    <p>as a memeber of the institute of new york, Clary can often be found training there or running missions with Jace, Izzy, & Alec.
</blockquote>

<p><b>option ii.</b> meeting in Alicante.
<blockquote>
    <p>infrequently, she has to travel to the Shadowhunter homeworld to settle business so it's possible to cross paths with her there during one such trip.
</blockquote>

<p><b>option iii.</b> meeting during her mundane life.
<blockquote>
    <p>unlike other shadowhunters, Clary was held back from her Nephilim heritage until she was 16 so there's always the possibility of her having crossed pathswith someone in her previous life.
</blockquote>

<p><b>option iv.</b> meeting in los angeles.
<blockquote>
    <p>as an adult, Clary infrequently assists the Institute of Los Angeles.
</blockquote>

<br>
<br>
<br />
<br />
<br />
<br />
</li>

<li>
<h4>headcanons</h4>

<p>- Clary is often said to look almost exactly like Jocelyn with their green eyes, curly red hair, slender figure, small chest & narrow hips, though she does not see it, nor does she see the beauty others often see in her. 

<p>- When she was younger, she gravitated towards more boyish clothes - baggy t-shirts, jeans, & sneakers being the primary parts of her wardrobe but as she grew older & spent more time around Isabelle, she's embraced the more feminine side of herself.

<p>- Clary has a white star-shaped scar on her shoulder because of her contact with the angel Ithuriel. She received her scar because she was born with Ithuriel's angel blood in her veins through Valentine's experiments.

<p>- Clary now goes by her mother's maiden name, <b>Fairchild</b>.

<p>- She cuts her own hair.

<p>For her mother and Luke's wedding, she painted a portrait of Luke & Jocelyn as a wedding gift.

<p>Though Shadowhunters do not celebrate Thanksgiving, Clary & Simon, having grown up mundane, missed it & started throwing their own Thanksgiving parties with their new friends & family. They've enjoyed introducing Jace, Izzy, Alec, & the others to such delicacies as green bean casserole & sweet potatoes with melted marshmallows.

<p>In 2010, Clary's soul attended the wedding of Tessa Gray & Jem Carstairs on Blackfriars Bridge in her dreams. It soon faded from her memory.
 
<br />
<br />
<br />
<br />
<br>
<br>

