<ul id="poptab">
<li class="active">
<h4>description</h4>
<p>After valentine was killed* during the uprising, Jocelyn, pregnant with Clary, took her growing family & left idris for paris. She would live there quietly for a number of years before it became apparent that simple discipline alone was not enough to curb the effects of the demon blood running in Jonathan's veins.

<p>When he was six, she realized she wouldn't be able to give him what he needed alone, & left paris to find old friends & allies. weeks later, the family <b>presented themselves to the lightwoods</b> at the new york institute, asking not only for shelter but for training for the boy, as well as eventually for his younger sister. the training was intense, but the two young fairchild children flourished within the confines of the Clave's outpost.

<br />
<br />
<br />
<br />
</li>

