<h4>notes on interaction</h4>

<p><center><h3>coming soon</h3></center>

<p><b>option i.</b> meeting during her time in the coven
<blockquote>
    <p>Clary stays with the coven for ten years - from six until sixteen - & the bulk of her training takes place here. She has access to the coven's grounds, but also can travel <b>somewhat</b> extensively given the Coven's funds so meeting somewhere in Eastern Europe is a definite possibility. 
</blockquote>
 
<p><b>option ii.</b> meeting after moving to NYC.
 <blockquote>
     <p>After Clary turns 16, she's revealed to the Clave & there's a custody hearing. Eventually, she's granted her freedom to move between Idris, New York, & Ördögház as needed so it's possible for her to meet anyone at sixteen once she's moved to the Institute of New York.
 </blockquote>
 
<p><b>option iii.</b> meeting originally as children
 <blockquote>
     <p>Clary lived in New York until she was six years old, & as such, she would only barely remember anyone she met during that time but the possibility exists - especially if she were to meet them again after having lived with the Coven for some time.
 </blockquote>
 
