<li>
<h4>headcanons</h4>

<p>- has trained alongside the <b>death dealers</b> from a young age, & intends to keep furthering her training as far as she can take it. 

<blockquote>
    <p>because of this training, she has a high proficiency for firearms even though they aren't Clave-sanctioned & do not typically work on demons.
</blockquote>

<p>- because of her unusually potent angelic blood, Clary's blood is <b>unappealing</b> to vampires - meaning one would have to be unusually desperate to be enticed by it. this is how she's been able to survive safely in the coven even when others are only minimally supervised by Sonja's most trusted coven members. 

<p>- As an added layer of protection, Jocelyn doesn't know the official location of the Old World Coven. Clary has been raised in <b>Ördögház, Hungary</b>, since she was a child. It's a city near the Hungarian city of Szentendre, between Budapest & the Pilis-Visegrád Mountains.

<p>- she can speak English, Hungarian, German, & Romanian.

