<li class="active">
<h4>description</h4>
<p><blockquote><b>important!</b> this verse is based as an extension of her <b>centurion</b> verse, found under her canon variants tab. all headcanons & notes prior to 2013 will carry over.</blockquote>

<p>After falling through a rift in space & time due to the <b>convergence</b> in 2013, Clary found herself in another New York so very unlike the world she had left behind. <b>Earth-199999</b>. 

<p>After wandering for what felt like a long time, cut off from the Shadoworld that no longer seemed to exist, she found herself swept up by <b>SHIELD</b>. Her unique abilities gave her a fighting edge, & she was recruited to work alongside other agents, as well as eventually working alongside the Avengers themselves.

<p>Because the Convergence only happens once every 5,000 years, it would seem it impossible for her to return home. It's a new world, & a new chance for change. She had wanted to leave behind a world that took almost everything from her, & so now she embraces this new timeline & hopes that maybe this time she can protect the things that matter to her the most. 
<br />
<br />
<br />
<br />
</li>

