</li>

<li>
<h4>headcanons</h4>
<p>while her first few lives & deaths occurred within the same geographic location, for some inexplicable reason her immortality is only fractionally complete. after being killed on the temple grounds in the 4<sup>th</sup> century CE, it would seem her immortality had been cut short, & she was finally ready to rest. not even she knows why she was allowed to be reborn four centuries later, or why her immortality <i>changed</i> to a cycle of rebirth.
<br />
<br />
