<h4>description</h4>
<p>She hadn't expected to get scouted for this particular project, but knowing the name behind it, it made a lot of sense. She'd been between gigs, working out of her mom & step-dad's place in Manhattan when <b>Alec Lightwood</b> had given her a call, offering her a spot on the underwater research station <i>mana one</i>. It would be a great gig, he promised - & somewhat of a reunion for the group that had worked out of the institute together for years.

<p><b>jace. alec. izzy. her brother. maia.</b> it felt a little too good to be true, but she'd accepted without too much hesitation. as an acquatic botanist & research biologist, the vibrant underwater life at the station means she has no shortage of projects she can work on. taking turns in the kitchen & in the gliders with her brother, their goal is to study the deep sea environments never before fully mapped with state of the art equipment supplied by <b>the Tanaka Institute</b>.... & programmed by one very mysterious <a href="https://bastxrds.tumblr.com/">Asajj Ventress</a>.
