<ul id="poptab">
<li class="active">
<h4>description</h4>

<blockquote>
    <p>This verse is a prequel re-imaging of her main <b>ASOIAF</b> verse.
</blockquote>

<p>after years of living on the run, Clary came to King's Landing by way of crossing the Narrow Sea after her mother was taken from their home when men in the service of her estranged husband attempted to reclaim the egg she had fled Asshai with years prior. It was a lucky thing, that egg - it <i>hatching</i> was the only way the little girl was able to get away from Pangborn & Blackwell. Selling what little the family had left, Clary made for King's Landing with <b>Tessys</b> - the dragon hatched from the egg.

<p>Now in King's Landing, Clary petitioned King Viserys to be allowed to remain at court as a dragonrider, & as lady to the royal household. At first it seemed it would work perfectly, but Tessys was far too headstrong a dragon to be contained - one evening, Tessys escaped the Dragonkeepers & bolted from the dragonpit. He hasn't been sighted since, & now Clary is alone in the Red Keep.

<br>
<br>
<br />
<br />
<br />
<br />
</li>
<li>
<h4>notes on interaction</h4>

<p><b>option i.</b> <i>meeting in King's Landing</i>
