<blockquote>
    <p>Given her status as a lady in the princess' service, it's plausible for her to be found at Dragonstone.
</blockquote>

<p><b>option iv.</b> <i>meeting in another city</i>.
<blockquote>
    <p>In the event that Clary is sent away from King's Landing, it's possible she & her mother would venture to any number of other cities within Westeros so this option is always available with plotting. 
</blockquote>

