<li>
<h4>headcanons</h4>

<p>- Clary is wholly unaware of her brother, who is <a href="https://affcgato.tumblr.com/post/651747955764838400/asshai-under-the-shadow-fandom-verse-jonathan">very much alive & well in Essos</a>. 

<p>- like her brother, Clary is a descendent of the Dragonlords - one of the noble families from the Valyrian Freehold. while she is aware of this fact - she was told in a letter that accompanied her dragon's egg, she doesn't speak of it & assumes it a moot point as she takes after her mother & lacks any significant features that would identify her as such.

<p>- Clary & her brother are descendants of <b>Aerea Targaryen</b>, the princess who disappeared for a year on the back of Balerion before returning to King's Landing near death. Balerion took the two of them back to Valyria, & upon seeing the wreckage, continued East - bringing them to Asshai. They were caught, & the princess was subjected to deep magic in the shadowlands, only escaping after the shadowbinders took what they needed from her.

<p>- This line would eventually give rise to her father Valentine, & Jonathan.

<p>- like her brother, Clary was also victim to her father's experimentations on her before she was born. she's unaware of this, or what it could mean for her. 

<br />
<br />

</li>

